headline: Meta's AI leaders discuss using Google, OpenAI models in apps, The Information says
summary: Leaders at Meta's new AI organization, Meta Superintelligence Labs, have explored integrating Google's Gemini model to deliver conversational, text-based responses for queries submitted to Meta AI, the company's primary chatbot, the report said.  Discussions have included leveraging OpenAI's models to power Meta AI and other AI features in Meta's social media apps, the Information added.
